CREATE TABLE `all_data_types` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sample_int` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_tinyint` tinyint DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_smallint` smallint DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_mediumint` mediumint DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_bigint` bigint DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_float` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_double` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_decimal` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_datetime` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_timestamp` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_year` year DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_char` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_varchar` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_blob` blob,
  `sample_text` text,
  `sample_tinyblob` tinyblob,
  `sample_tinytext` tinytext,
  `sample_mediumblob` mediumblob,
  `sample_mediumtext` mediumtext,
  `sample_longblob` longblob,
  `sample_longtext` longtext,
  `sample_enum` enum('x','y','z') DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_set` set('a','b','c') DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_bit` bit(8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_binary` binary(8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_varbinary` varbinary(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_geometry` geometry DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_boolean` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sample_json` json DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=11 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci

CREATE TABLE `debezium_signals` (
  `id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `data` varchar(2048) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
